# Configure your host name

@apimHostname = <your-api-management-instance-name>.azure-api.net



#===============================================================================
# Protected API - Requests to directly call the Protected API on APIM
#===============================================================================

### Validates client certificate using validate-client-certificate policy

GET https://{{apimHostname}}/protected/validate-using-policy


### Validates client certificate using the context.Request.Certificate property

GET https://{{apimHostname}}/protected/validate-using-context



#===============================================================================
# Unprotected API - Requests to call the Protected API via the Unprotected API
#===============================================================================

### Call validate-client-certificate on Protected API via Unprotected API

GET https://{{apimHostname}}/unprotected/validate-using-policy


### Call validate-using-context on Protected API via Unprotected API

GET https://{{apimHostname}}/unprotected/validate-using-context
